snippet.title: Johnny Depp Speaks On Amber Heard Ruining Her Own Career
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Speaks On Amber Heard Ruining Her Own Career

Johnny Depp and Amber Heard used to beTHAT it couple in Hollywood wherein people think they would live happily ever after. But sadly, this is not the case anymore. From an A-list star falling in love with an up-and-coming ingenue on set to allegations of abuse emerging, this story just doesn’t happen in normal life. This also happens behind the cameras.

In the previous years, people turned against Johnny Depp as it was rumored that he was the abusive one in their relationship. But in reality, it's the other way around.
